    "type": "spell",
    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Siphoning negative energy into yourself, your hand radiates a pale darkness. Your touch weakens the living and disorients undead, possibly even causing them to flee. The effect depends on whether the target is living or undead.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Living Creature</strong> The spell deals negative damage equal to 1d4 plus your spellcasting modifier. The target attempts a basic Fortitude save, but is also @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled} 1 for 1 round on a critical failure.</li>\n<li><strong>Undead Creature</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Flat-Footed} for 1 round on a failed Fortitude save. On a critical failure, the target is also @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.sDPxOjQ9kx2RZE8D]{Fleeing} for 1 round unless it succeeds at a Will save.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The negative damage to living creatures increases by 1d4.</p>",
